Role Description
This is a part-time, remote role for a team member dedicated to supporting our mission of delivering impactful career development tips. Responsibilities include researching and developing high-quality, engaging content for our LinkedIn audience, strategizing new ideas to expand our reach, collaborating with our team on innovative campaigns, and maintaining a cohesive content plan. Candidates will also analyze audience engagement data to refine and improve content strategies.

